_:Nac50fa1e6d984fc0b444584cb168e678 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Claire Hughes was appointed Parliamentary Under-Secretary of State in the Wales Office and Assistant Whip, House of Commons on 16 September 2025.</p>\n\n<p>She was previously Junior Lord of the Treasury (Government Whip) between 7 September 2025 and 16 September 2025.</p>\n\n<p>She was elected as the MP for Bangor Aberconwy in July 2024.</p>\n" <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/jsonld> .
